    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Renggeria comans are bronchitis, which it has been proven to alleviate by reducing inflammation in the airways. It has been used to treat fever, particularly in cases of malaria, by lowering body temperature and reducing symptoms. The plant is also effective in treating fungal infections, including athlete's foot, by inhibiting the growth of fungi. Additionally, Renggeria comans has been shown to reduce swelling and ease pain associated with arthritis. Furthermore, it has been used to treat stomach ulcers by protecting the mucous membranes in the stomach and reducing inflammation.",
